UDP Return Path for Packet Loss and
Delay Measurement for MPLS Networks
2016", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7876.html", target="_top", tooltip="RFC 6374 defines a protocol for Packet Loss and Delay Measurement for MPLS networks (MPLS-PLDM).  This document specifies the procedures to be used when sending and processing out-of-band MPLS performance management Responses over an UDP/IP return path."];
